net.fec.openrq

Class SerializablePacket

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.fec.openrq.SerializablePacket
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class SerializablePacket
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A serializable encoding packet.

    This class serializes a FEC Payload ID, and an array of bytes containing encoding symbols (see class EncodingPacket).

    See Also:
    EncodingPacket, Serialized Form
